text: For Those Who Can Tell No Tales is a 2013 Bosnian Qatari German drama movie directed by Jasmila Žbanić and starring Kym Vercoe, Boris Isaković, Simon McBurney, Branko Cvejić, Leon Lučev, Pamela Rabe. ==Other websites== * Category:2013 drama movies Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina movies Category:Qatari movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies directed by Jasmila Žbanić
title: For Those Who Can Tell No Tales
